<h4 class="tabtitle">About Us </h4>
<pre class="tabcontent">Here at Budget Golf, we want to provide all golfers, men, women, and juniors with quality products at budget prices. We shop for deals so we can pass on the savings to you. Customer satisfaction is our number 1 priority whether we are custom making a new set, repairing your old set, or helping you plan your next golf outing. We invite you to come to us for all of your golfing needs and we guarantee you will receive the utmost in customer service. That is our goal! 
So whether you are looking for that perfect gift for someone special or 100 dozen logo golf balls for your company, we can handle just about anything pertaining to the game of golf. We have been in the Golf Business for over 20 years. 
Please give us a call at 815-630-2098 or email us at ebay at budget golf dot com.  
We always strive to have our customers leave with a positive experience. We treat every case in a fair and honest manner. Service is our Most Important Product.
