<h4 class="tabtitle">Payments </h4>
<pre class="tabcontent">Payments must be made via Paypal within 5 business days of the auction ending or But it Now order is submitted. If payment is not made within 5 business days, a non paying bidder alert with eBay will be submitted. We only accept Paypal for payment. There are no exceptions. 
Combined invoices into one payment can be done if requested. If needed, please contact us by contacting seller and sending us an eBay message. Once a payment is made, no order can be canceled or modified. We strive to have a very fast turnaround time. Once a payment is made the order is processed and shipped right away. 
Invoices are sent electronically as well by email. No invoices will be enclosed within the package. 
</pre>
