<h4 class="tabtitle">Shipping</h4>
<pre class="tabcontent">All orders are shipped within 24 hours of the order being received. Many times, any order placed by 1pm CST will ship the same day. Shipments are made to the address received on the Paypal invoice at the time of purchase only. No address changes will be made once an order is submitted. If an address change is needed, it would need to be done through Paypal prior to payment. 
Tracking information is sent automatically via email once generated. A tracking notice will be sent to the email address on file with eBay and a notice should also be found in your My eBay section as well. We only ship to the lower 48 states in the U.S. Hawaii and Alaska would need additional shipping costs. If an item has Free Shipping it will only apply to the lower 48 states as well. 
We only ship via UPS ground shipping. All packages will be shipped ground. There are no in store/local pick up options. All packages are shipped out with UPS. 
All of our packages are generated automatically with a flat rate 1 pound label. They are then weighed again once they arrive at the UPS facility. Please disregard the weight as it does not reflect or indicate the actual weight or contents. 
Due to the volume of our shipping, we ship our products out in pallet form and a UPS semi picks them up. They go straight to the largest UPS facility in the country. They do not go directly to a UPS hub where they scan every package. This is why you may not see all of the shipment progress. There may be occasions where tracking updates are not visible until the day of arrival. 
We do not ship to P.O Boxes or APO addresses. We wish UPS shipped to those locations, but unfortunately, they do not. We only ship to physical addresses and physical addresses are needed for shipment. 
If you purchase something on the weekend, you may receive a tracking notice but progress may not be updated until the following business day. 
Signature Required - As per Paypal and eBay policy, any order over $250 or any international shipment will be signature required. We cannot alter this policy. It is simply for security purposes. Please keep that in mind when ordering. 
Combined Shipping - If possible, we will try to combine shipping. Not all items are able to be combined. Please email us with what you would like and we will be happy to see what we can do. Orders are not guaranteed to be combined as all orders are processed once a payment is made. We can only combine orders if no payment is received. 
Shipments in transit - In some cases, orders can be redirected through UPS. A fee is needed for this service. Or, we can have a package held for pick up at a UPS location closes to the original shipping address for no additional fee. Those are the only two options. If a package is returned to our location due to being not delivered, a message will be sent to arrange alternate options. A fee will be needed as well in this instance. 
International Shipping - International orders can be completed through the eBay Global Shipping Program. This is a service provided by eBay directly. We ship the package to an eBay location, and they complete the international portion. Additional shipping time is needed to allow for this. 
</pre>
