<h4 class="tabtitle">Returns & Exchanges</h4>
<pre class="tabcontent">As long as the item is still new and unused you are welcome to send back the item for either a refund or exchange. All items are under the EBay return policy with a money back option within 14 days of purchase so long as the item is still in the same condition that it was received. 
All items can only be returned if still new and unused and in the same condition as they were received. All items must be returned in its original packaging with tags if applicable. All Returns/Exchanges are subject to a 20% Re-stocking Fee.   
 
For exchanges, please contact us and we can provide a return form that can be included with the returned item. An exchange can either be done by filling out the form and noting the requested item to be exchanged for. Or, a new order can be made right away, and noted on the form that a duplicate order was done and a return for refund is requested. 
For refunds, customers can request return labels from the eBay Managed Returns Experience. Buyers can print a return label, select a cause for return, track status, see the estimated return amount, and are protected by the returns policy. Buyers will go to the Returns section of eBay to initiate that process. 
Shipping and Handling charges are non refundable. If shipping was free, actual cost will be deducted from any refund. We do not receive any type of refund from UPS, therefore that charge will be deducted. 
To assist in the return/exchange process, please include a copy of your invoice or packing slip with the completed form back to us. All packages, especially shoes must be packaged in some kind of packaging rather than simply placing a shipping label directly onto the box/product. 
